@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Completed : cancel
Completed --> Archived : reject
Archived --> Reviewed : process
Reviewed --> Draft : reject
Reviewed : entry / log medicalrecord
Draft --> Created : reject
Draft : entry / log medicalrecord
Created --> [*]
@enduml